<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <p>您好:</p>

      <p>订单<%= @order.code %><%if @order.state == "proof_unapproved"%>的排期表<% end %>链接为：<%if @order.state == "proof_unapproved"%>http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/orders/scheduling?id=<%=@order.id%><%else%>http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/orders/<%=@order.id%><%end%>
      </p>
      <p>
        订单状态为：<span style="color:red;"><%= I18n.t @order.state%></span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <% if @order.state == "proof_unapproved" %>
        以下为排期表详情:
        <% else %>
        以下为订单详情：
        <% end %>
      </p>
      <div>
        <%if @order.whether_service?%>
            <%= render :partial => "service_order_template",:object=>@order %>
        <%else %>
            <%= render :partial => "order_template",:object=>@order %>
            <%= render :partial => "advertisement_template",:object=>@order %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>谢谢</p>

      <p>爱点击互动</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

